Form 1:
Text field: Enter URL or start typing below
Submit button
Form 1 calls the getURLSentiment API route

Form 2
Text Area: No placeholder
Submit button
Form 2 calls the getTextSentiment API route

print response as JSON string in the div id="response" of the page -->
